docs {
  # Add Item to List
  
  Add a new item to a shopping list.
  
  ## Path Parameters
  
  - `familyId`: ID of the family
  - `listId`: ID of the shopping list
  
  ## Request Body
  
  - `name` (string, required): Name of the item (1-200 characters)
  
  ## Response
  
  Returns the updated shopping list with the new item added.
  
  Each item contains:
  - `_id`: Unique item identifier
  - `name`: Item name
  - `checked`: Boolean (false by default)
  - `createdAt`: Item creation timestamp
  
  ## Status Codes
  
  - `201`: Item added successfully
  - `400`: Validation error
  - `401`: Unauthorized (missing or invalid token)
  - `403`: Forbidden (not a family member)
  - `404`: Shopping list not found
}
